# Environment

Copy `.env.example` to `.env.local` for local development.

```bash
RESEND_API_KEY=re_xxxxxxxx
# Must be the Resend account email until a domain is verified:
CONTACT_TO_EMAIL=jonahthomaslloydhughes@gmail.com
# Optional once you verify a domain in Resend:
# CONTACT_FROM_EMAIL=JTLH LTD <hello@yourdomain.com>
# CONTACT_TO_EMAIL=jtlhltd@gmail.com
```

Without `RESEND_API_KEY`, the contact form returns 503.
